Description
THE DATE FOR THE FORENSICS TOWNHALL HAS BEEN POSTPONED TO 8 DEC 25 From 11 AM to 12 PM.  
The newly formed NIEMOpen Forensics Sub-Committee invites you to their first TOWHALL event. This is your opportunity to meet the Forensics team and learn about their organization and activities associated with NIEMOpen.
 



Meeting Agenda: Dec. 8, 2025 11am – 11:40am
Opening Remarks – Ryan Triplett
NIEMOpen Introduction and Brief History – Paul Warmelli
NIEMOpen Forensic Team intro - Ryan Triplett
Cochair Introductions
NIEMOpen Forensic Overview - Ryan Triplett
NIEMOpen Forensic Data Model and Tiger Teams Overview – Eleanor Harner
NIEMOpen Forensic Town Hall Closing Remarks - Ryan Triplett

Action Items:
Meeting slides distributed to attendees
Next Meeting in January – Review Forensic data model and attributes for submission

Attendees: 67 attendees on ZOOM Call
